headline: Veralto (VLTO): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: Veralto trades at $107.37 and has moved in lockstep with the market. Its shares have returned 7.6% over the last six months while the S&P 500 has gained 8.8%.
